# Command Center

Parent intelligence layer for Smart Lodge. Widget specs live in `docs/command-center-widgets/`.

## Principles

- Parent page shows summaries only; details open via `/command-center/{view}` or child module routes.
- Decision-support only — no auto-execution of high-impact ops without approval.
- KPIs aggregate from Room Utilization and Housekeeping services when seeded data exists.

## Routes

- `/command-center` — main dashboard
- `/command-center/alerts`, `ai-recommendations`, `module-health`, etc. — detail views
- Child modules: `dashboard`, `room-utilization`, `housekeeping-planning`

Match existing LodgeX Inertia + React patterns. Minimize diffs.
